node.text:
UNDENIABLY GIFTED🎁
Here go a raw display of raw talent.⭐️

Anyone who done been to one of my tour shows know I like to bring different elements of entertainment to the
stage so we had fun with this one. 

Shoutout to every position played on stage during this performance, it trip me out how easy we make that shit look. 
Pay attention to the errors & adjustments made in real time without compromising the performance, it don’t matter if a dinosaur walk in we bet not EVER stop nigga!

I enjoy challenging y’all with more creative ways to utilize y’all gift while y’all make me raise the bar for myself. 

Y’all bring the Mega-Star out of a nigga.💪🏾

ALBUM & TOUR date announcements coming soon MF. 
Can’t wait to pop it🗣😊

#LIVESHOWKILLA

node.text:
Left a studio session full of SLEEPY ass niggas in Miami like 8am after recording all night, & pulled straight up on da 🐐himself, watched bruh walk dat shit down right there in front of me at 10:30 in da morning & walk out the booth w/ the straight face talkin bout “you fw dat?” 

FYM NIGGA?! 😂🔥

We ain’t finna act like you ain’t LIL WAYNE bruh🐐

Preciate you to say the least. Nigga can’t tell me shit, ’m “Best Rapper Alive approved” ✅.

“Lonely”  Me & @liltunechi . Out NOW!
